SampleLocationDescription.item: Sample taken from peat bog near Southernmost tip of island, surrounded by fresh moss tundra (Rhacomitrium canescens, Salix polaris, Ptilidium ciliare, and Oxyria digyna) and snow-bed tundra (Cerastium regelii, Drepanocladus revolvens, Cochlearia groenlandica, and Drepanocladus uncinatus).
